#: 5b2ca5993a62460995ad22a89b8afc5a
msgid "Get a list of VM disks using ``sudo lvs``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/troubleshooting/disk-troubleshooting.rst:62
#: 553f93be47d549adadf97ae3085a2677
msgid ""
"Use ``sudo lvremove qubes_dom0/<name>`` to remove backup copies of some "
"less important VMs – entries with ``-back`` in their name."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/troubleshooting/disk-troubleshooting.rst:64
#: 6f139f82ed4d4a3ca2235f123261105a
msgid ""
"If that isn’t enough, remove actual disks of less important VMs. NOTE: "
"You will lose the data of that VM, but your system will resume working."
msgstr ""

